Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:20.06,mianze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(160,500)}翻译:娜娜莉  校译:小呆 时间&特效:幽幽子 打杂:面麻酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 烫烫烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「请吃吧」还得意洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 我忽然觉得好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 感觉怪难受的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波个头最大 那就给你最大的那个 给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「波波个头最大」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经长这么壮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 太好吃了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢 给我最怎样的呢 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给雪集的是葡萄干最多的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 我希望你能直接告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 纸 纸 还有笔 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个写出面麻的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 写不出来啊仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 明明都写在日记本上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨水还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再试一次 给我 我再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子 好难受 鹤…子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 现在好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 感觉全身无力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 没有生我们的气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经原谅我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有没有原谅我们 我们无从知道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她还生气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里还会给我们做什么蒸面包…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许正是因为她还没有原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了责备我们 才出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种可能也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能写字的话 一开始就写出来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有道理 那样的话我们也能交流 也能立刻相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为仁碳和面麻 都挺笨的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 说什么要相信面麻的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果不还是自己独占了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城 存好打工钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花 我们要做给她看 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要 让面麻成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折腾得那么厉害 也难怪会累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家打算要做烟花 为了让你…成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子…就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 跑太快的话危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅…原谅喜欢仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…果然还是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有放弃…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的轮班 能不能和我换一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮班？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周四 桥那边有个工程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日薪挺高的 所以周四想去那里打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算玩腻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:49.68,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个啊 那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是她... 芽衣子的母亲和山先生联系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 叔叔您 并不反对烟花的事情对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还活在过去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子变成那样之后 她的时间就停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她拉回到现实中来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我不想让她再回忆起来更多了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨的想法可能有些可笑 但我觉得我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 喜欢您的女儿 喜欢芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了芽衣子 我想做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还活在过去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然会做出这么没面子的事情 真让我惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一点没变啊 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了面麻的话什么都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信的话就可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让面麻成佛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么地在意面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明通过宿海就可以和她交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过宿海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 接下来要去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为今晚也会干到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这之前 先把面麻送回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 不想总憋在屋里 我去哪儿都要跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 想和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 她说「想和大家一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 还是留着长发吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯 说起来她和我们一样也在成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成长…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁会喜欢她这丑女…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 一般般…漂亮… 还是该说是可爱型的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是一般般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你个呆子 笨蛋 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一般般啦 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像是在演独角戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 并不是那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.77,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9话「大家和面麻」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你们做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了 cool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过火药必须由我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的地方 你们试着帮帮忙如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这太吓人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个会从竹筒里出来对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色多点的话 看起来比较可爱 感觉应该会不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？ 你还真是和给人的形象不一样呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在这里点火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 那么这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那里只是装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了抬上发射台的时候方便点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.23,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面麻 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放手啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她跑你背上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 面麻 你饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:56.23,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波波波 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 明明看不到 却又能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比不过她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是 现在也是 一直比不过她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去买点果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚才也差点就喊出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻还在我们身边 我认同了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 却看不到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连交谈也办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想再见面麻一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么只有宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对宿海也是 果然还是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚还叫着仁碳 一下就换成宿海了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么吗 你那一幅已经看透别人心思的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看透的也就只有你 是相似的人之间产生的共鸣之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你这种性格恶劣的人相似 绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我说过的那件事 那个事 我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩要不要试着交往一下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是对男孩子没有抵抗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的中段踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 什么漂亮的中段踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笑的时候啊 我真的吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么令你吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 燃起干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 安鸣的布偶不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 突然间就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是反复无常的小猫咪啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果啊 如果面麻真的在仁碳那的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望实现了以后面麻不就消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到该打工的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 面麻你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和波波一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想留在这里 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎欢迎 热烈欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闹得太凶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴…啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.44,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 那个 我看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 我还以为是夏天的猛兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在都已经是穿冬装的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.29,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香港 与僵尸战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 写上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.26,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 你太厉害了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是在家的本子上却写不上 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多写点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说点什么吧 多多益善
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…你对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 对了 玩接龙吗 画画接龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么啊 好像金楚糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双带背包 红宝石…石…玻璃球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽欧…欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手上的纹和纹对起来就是 幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望远镜 面麻队员开始进行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:14.83,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拨打的号码现在不在服务区或已经关机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 打不通 还在打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要走得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她应该 在秘密基地那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么 这么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 面麻消失什么的 绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对绝对不要让仁碳死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不才是都已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说别人奇怪的人自己才是怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:19:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 有鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河里 有很大一条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻我啊 想靠近看一看 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在树根那里 一摇一摆的 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你在撒娇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一直…一直留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待…待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去抓那条鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 这样你会弄湿的 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 傻瓜仁碳 会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仁碳


Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:32.39,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君と夏の終わり 将来の夢 大きな希望 忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.23,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}10年後の8月 また出会えるのを信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:47.56,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}最高の思い出を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:56.01,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}出会いはふっとした瞬間 帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:01.71,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}声をかけてくれたね 「一緒に帰ろう」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}あぁ 花火が夜空 きれいに咲いて ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}あぁ 風が時間とともに流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:10.12,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}嬉しくって 楽しくって 冒険もいろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:16.91,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}二人の秘密の基地の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:24.29,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君と夏の終わり 将来の夢 大きな希望 忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:31.37,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}10年後の8月 また出会えるのを信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:38.60,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君が最後まで心から「ありがとう」叫んでたこと知ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:45.64,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}涙をこらえて 笑顔でさようなら せつないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:52.83,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}最高の思い出を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:32.39,ED-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}难忘与你共度的夏末 未来的梦想 大大的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.23,ED-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}坚信10年后的8月 我们还能重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:47.56,ED-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}珍藏最美的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:56.01,ED-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}相遇只在蓦然的瞬间 回家的十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:01.71,ED-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}你对我说「一起回家吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}啊 烟花华丽地绽放夜空 些许伤感
